{"tid":1544624,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【反送中】浸大有賤人中國女人撕完文宣之後搶人手機","createTime":"2019-09-05T15:26:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T02:14:17.000Z","uid":145996,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"84808633886c05503df6866dfe75907416db17eb","tid":1544624,"uid":145996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T15:26:54.000Z","msg":"【浸大編委訊】有一名內地生晚上9時15分在呂明才中心九樓撕海報，有同學在場阻止並錄影但遭其搶手機，該女子迅速被大量同學包圍。學生事務處輔導長鄧裕南教授到場調停。在場同學高叫「還電話」，該同學一度掩耳，惟圍觀的同學愈加高呼。<br />\n<br />\n事件發生至今超過兩小時，學生會會長方仲賢呼籲輔導長鄧裕南聯絡周偉立副校長，盡快到場處理事件，否則叫記者進場，惟鄧只一直安撫該中國女生，未有理會在場同學訴求。<br />\n<br />\n另，在場同學指，因不想警察進入校園，故此暫時未有報警，會等肇事女子交還手機後將她送出學校門口上警車。"},{"pid":"6515ee96768854a213dfb21a9ebf78078b5c8a94","tid":1544624,"uid":257422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T15:27:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人<br />\n約定你<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aTJem7g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaTJem7g.jpg&h=c2ef69f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e91jFMP.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe91jFMP.gif&h=6056e7b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n九月八日 星期日<br />\n絕對和理非<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><br />\n12:00pm <br />\n遮打集合<br />\n<br />\n2:00pm<br />\n<ins>美國駐港澳總領事館</ins> <br />\n為《香港人權及民主法案》請願</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">聽熟國歌未？<br />\n好撚好聽<br />\n到時一齊唱 ：</span></span><br />\n<br />\nOh, say can you see,<br />\nBy the dawn's early light,<br />\nWhat so proudly we hailed,<br />\nAt the twilight's last gleaming?&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/PWMy7Rpk5Bo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FPWMy7Rpk5Bo&d=t4s0zgtGzRvDs5iH%2BzYNWPYtrFBHe52Fn%2F6n3rMGN5k%3D&h=38e3